{"tid":767024,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《蜘蛛俠2》港台譯名被彈","createTime":"2018-08-04T06:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T23:03:47.000Z","uid":105567,"like":4,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":125,"replies":[{"pid":"2024320a5c17bee5b9d3a7b0284eb3e2340968a4","tid":767024,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180803/20467240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180803%2F20467240&d=ZOwk2VD1aPyj0iYDXd08dJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8495cb48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180803%2F20467240&h=13137ed7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180803/20467240</a><br />\n<br />\nMarvel與Sony聯手打造的蜘蛛俠電影大受歡迎，第二集《Spider-Man：Far From Home》亦已在拍攝中。而今集的港版譯名亦出爐，名叫《蜘蛛俠：決戰千里》，但網民似乎覺得有陣陣娘味。不過港版都不及台版譯名古怪，因台版將之譯為《蜘蛛人：離家日》。另外，男主角湯姆賀倫（Tom Holland）昨日於Ig發放片場片段，片中見到他的戰衣與上集一樣，並未有新衣登場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url]<img src=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/51b3dc8ee4b051b96ceb10de/t/5b61e28e562fa79f0e7683be/1533141652864/the-official-logo-for-spider-man-far-from-home-has-been-revealed?format=2500w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F51b3dc8ee4b051b96ceb10de%2Ft%2F5b61e28e562fa79f0e7683be%2F1533141652864%2Fthe-official-logo-for-spider-man-far-from-home-has-been-revealed%3Fformat%3D2500w&h=76ce729b&s={SIZE}\" />[/url]"},{"pid":"ce8ad45900a144853407ae71db05f8b2bdf93ca4","tid":767024,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef29c05f24132500b55976cbd326d18d5a23570e","tid":767024,"uid":34525,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy