m/entertainment/daily/article/20180803/20467240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180803%2F20467240&d=ZOwk2VD1aPyj0iYDXd08dJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8495cb48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180803%2F20467240&h=13137ed7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180803/20467240</a><br />\n<br />\nMarvel與Sony聯手打造的蜘蛛俠電影大受歡迎，第二集《Spider-Man：Far From Home》亦已在拍攝中。而今集的港版譯名亦出爐，名叫《蜘蛛俠：決戰千里》，但網民似乎覺得有陣陣娘味。不過港版都不及台版譯名古怪，因台版將之譯為《蜘蛛人：離家日》。另外，男主角湯姆賀倫（Tom Holland）昨日於Ig發放片場片段，片中見到他的戰衣與上集一樣，並未有新衣登場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url]<img src=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/51b3dc8ee4b051b96ceb10de/t/5b61e28e562fa79f0e7683be/1533141652864/the-official-logo-for-spider-man-far-from-home-has-been-revealed?format=2500w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F51b3dc8ee4b051b96ceb10de%2Ft%2F5b61e28e562fa79f0e7683be%2F1533141652864%2Fthe-official-logo-for-spider-man-far-from-home-has-been-revealed%3Fformat%3D2500w&h=76ce729b&s={SIZE}\" />[/url]"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T00:30:31.000Z","msg":"決戰千里同far from home啱啱調轉喎<br />\n夫運籌策帷帳之中，決勝於千里之外<br />\n係講係屋企坐係到，嘴炮指揮就打爆你"},{"pid":"8012aa505c397f1e368a1a9b7011ba9b5b657103","tid":767024,"uid":4349,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T00:36:13.000Z","msg":"又歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍親落去歐洲都好易變爛片<br />\n雷神2<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43588f1cb901e9db833ee73bf345846b8f9ebb98","tid":767024,"uid":82229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":